      "content": "thanks for that, it's a bit faster but i just tried running it against the massive test cases the prof sent and it's still hitting the timeout error. it's like it takes forever when the number is huge. can u make it even better? i really need to pass this before midnight or i'm gonna tank my grade. can u just make sure it finishes within the time limit no matter what?",
